{"tid":864754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬價值的藝術品經拍賣後，即時自動自毀","createTime":"2018-10-16T12:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T15:13:45.000Z","uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"624d534a28a181991c287829876e06954341a385","tid":864754,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"畫作落槌後自毀 Banksy拍片承認數年前暗藏碎紙機<br />\n <br />\n英國著名塗鴉大師班克斯 (Banksy) 作品「Girl with a Balloon」(2006) 上周五 (5日) 在倫敦蘇富比當代藝術晚拍上落槌一刻，隨即在眾目睽睽下自毀，被畫框內隱藏的碎紙機碎成條狀。班克斯其後在IG上載影片，承認自己在數年前已暗中把碎紙機藏在畫框內，計劃在完成拍賣的一刻將其碎成條狀，最終「陰謀」得逞。<br />\n<br />\n班克斯在描述中引用畢加索名言「破壞的衝動也是創造的衝動 (The urge to destroy is also a creative urge)」，並附上講解影片。片中先指他在數年前暗中在畫框中加裝了碎紙機，一旦畫作被拿去拍賣&amp;hellip;&amp;hellip;」然後一一名面部被打格的人，在畫框的底部裝上多塊鋒利刀片並重新組裝成晝框。<br />\n<br />\n接著便是拍賣會的現場畫面，「Girl with a Balloon」最後以連佣金的1,042,000英鎊 (約1,071萬港元) 成交。就在落槌一刻，作品的畫框響起警報，裝表於框內的「Girl with a Balloon」隨即滑落，同時被畫框內隱藏的碎紙機破壞。在場人士無不嘩然，工作人員其後移走該畫。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在IG留言讚揚班克斯，亦有人指今次事件傳達出「金錢不能買到一切」的訊息。蘇富比歐洲當代藝術部主管Alex Branczik在事後形容「被Banksy」(Banksy-ed)，慨嘆親身經歷了Banksy的天才。Branczik估計是Banksy本人親自按下遙控碎掉畫作，他還認為作品雖已自毀，但有了這經歷可能更顯矜貴。蘇富比未有進一步透露買家身份，有關拍賣是否維持有效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singtao.com.au/172-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82/643494-%E7%95%AB%E4%BD%9C%E8%90%BD%E6%A7%8C%E5%BE%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%AF%80-Banksy%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E6%9A%97%E8%97%8F%E7%A2%8E%E7%B4%99%E6%A9%9F/?fromG=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.com.au%2F172-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%2F643494-%25E7%2595%25AB%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A7%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AF%2580-Banksy%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259A%2597%25E8%2597%258F%25E7%25A2%258E%25E7%25B4%2599%25E6%25A9%259F%2F%3FfromG%3D1&d=cUe2kGK3L7mzwis%2B9D76sf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=49b1254b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.com.au/172-%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82/643494-%E7%95%AB%E4%BD%9C%E8%90%BD%E6%A7%8C%E5%BE%8C%E8%87%AA%E6%AF%80-Banksy%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E6%9A%97%E8%97%8F%E7%A2%8E%E7%B4%99%E6%A9%9F/?fromG=1</a>"},{"pid":"e0cea2455fc894bbd1f842c9b47d09f4c78cfe9e","tid":864754,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:12:21.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"eb630a18d0fa4254e977b77787a0b5ba36a741c9","tid":864754,"uid":31429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:12:46.000Z","msg":"!MOM"},{"pid":"67682fcffa196da3ea4672fd0dc146f7a0c93d58","tid":864754,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v-grdlU12Dw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv-grdlU12Dw&d=cUe2kGK3L7mzwis%2B9D76sf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6f41084d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v-grdlU12Dw</a>"},{"pid":"7dcba628dfac9a9e5017d889e2b0b82488b0cadf","tid":864754,"uid":17628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:17:28.000Z","msg":"成兩星期前已經熱烈討論完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb889985d91d70361aba6da94fb3f0e60f064b1","tid":864754,"uid":86097,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e59a4c1af2a6311a5bdd4f580f9354dff5b64c15","tid":864754,"uid":128325,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"今次樓主真係潮撚過潮洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44281d3d4735c0620dd1b7090544bbe4777aaca","tid":864754,"uid":182499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7fb889985d91d70361aba6da94fb3f0e60f064b1","tid":864754,"uid":86097,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"你今年幾歲？"},{"pid":"48ca86b0c44ae3f82a